ActPublic Service Staff Relations Act
PrecisAppointment of EVELYNE HENRYof Cumberland, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of fourteen months; and orders that she shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective July 6, 2003.
